<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />Sing to God! Sing praises to his name!</para>

<para style="q1">Praise the one who rides through the plains of the Jordan River valley!</para>

<para style="q1">Yahweh is his name! Rejoice before him!</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />A father of the fatherless, a judge of the widows,</para>

<para style="q1">is God in the holy place where he lives.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />God puts the lonely into families;</para>

<para style="q1">he brings out the prisoners with singing;</para>

<para style="q1">but the rebellious live in a parched land.</para>

